{"tid":292432,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"秋葵屎先係屎中極品","createTime":"2017-06-21T11:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T01:32:25.000Z","uid":115,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed2956869fdc15d45320c60c0a4e9522e9db588c","tid":292432,"uid":115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"呢排行過街市，口多多問下阿姐有咩當造<br />\n阿姐話初夏既秋葵最靚，有益健康 又乜又染<br />\n好似仲話咩食左碌鳩識轉彎<br />\n我份人又冇咩所謂，見阿姐落足嘴頭<br />\n平平地咁買左$20，已經有一大堆<br />\n<br />\n番到屋企就好似煮菜咁，加鹽加油 淥佢一陣<br />\n再整多個酸辣醬汁，加多枝大青島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一邊R住肚腩，一邊睇愛回家<br />\n<br />\n第一次食秋葵，又幾過癮<br />\n淡淡清新瓜味，口感幾爽<br />\n而且入面d籽幾有口感<br />\n但尾部 尖端有點苦<br />\n切開會有少少黏液，應該是精華黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知半夜訓訓下極肚痛<br />\n未落床已經痛到彎哂身<br />\n好彩屋企細，但到廁所門口已經feel到括約筋抽蓄<br />\n即是二邊屎忽係咁震<br />\n一除條褲 就好似跑馬咁，d屎係咁衝出黎<br />\n爽撚到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成件事唔洗二分鐘<br />\n感覺個肚好空虛<br />\n但係個人聰明左，行路又快<br />\n好似係<br />\n最緊要發現到d屎有一粒粒白色秋葵籽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/192539_0c01a37505dd0510c3ff7b028f8724e1.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F192539_0c01a37505dd0510c3ff7b028f8724e1.jpg&d=ISdeuin%2BCt4GA%2BY9SdWPfjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=d844f876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/192539_0c01a37505dd0510c3ff7b028f8724e1.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/192541_21246d8c20caef9e27268e04cac2acfa.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F192541_21246d8c20caef9e27268e04cac2acfa.jpg&d=ISdeuin%2BCt4GA%2BY9SdWPfjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=7e5745b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/192541_21246d8c20caef9e27268e04cac2acfa.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"3b671afb7f9eaa76039823d482659eeddea37cdf","tid":292432,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:27:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53bb7a5a2db1811af7d551e1dcb6bc31105f3c9d","tid":292432,"uid":115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:28:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>( Show Blocked User - 膊頭有花 )</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母！<br />\n又要睇又要block"},{"pid":"f4063b4d9c7d588b363c24fe67a0062529de1fa3","tid":292432,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10840e641ecdb143a421a32bce4e9bd494fdd999","tid":292432,"uid":7130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41044f672bfef35245cbb024c8d761ca7520690b","tid":292432,"uid":115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:32:27.000Z","msg":"我決定每星期食一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16ceaa997cf623035456b952be12c397102e9a9","tid":292432,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:32:35.000Z","msg":"有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7679fff01ef2d